      <title>商业地产风险拖累 NYCB 转型之路崎岖不平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/nycb-turnaround-faces-rocky-road-commercial-real-estate-exposure-drag-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约社区银行的扭亏为盈可能需要很长时间，因为分析师预计，由于银行努力增加其商业房地产投资组合中潜在不良贷款的准备金，利润仍将面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/nycb-turnaround-faces-rocky-road-commercial-real-estate-exposure-drag-2024-03-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 16:52:11 GMT</pubDate>
